{"tid":45004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲乜撚野創世乜春，王國乜乜 收皮未","createTime":"2016-12-18T16:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T20:49:44.000Z","uid":55514,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a39c41025497de65d654a2f3055e4cf85d727514","tid":45004,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"成日想上youtube睇下片，聽下歌放鬆下<br />\n你老味條條片都放廣告，<br />\n果創世乜尻，放條暴龍出黎轉轉轉，跟住有條女打交斗，跟住老江湖咁下體射死光，廣告黎架咩?浪費我時間炸掛<br />\n跟住果個王國乜乜，日尻日搵啲人黎講點好挽點好挽，之後仲要on99咁配啲完全唔夾嘅粵語<br />\n先唔理隻game係點，日尻日播廣告已經覺得好煩膠，你以為日日咁洗我腦就會玩呀?國教呀依家?<br />\n我絕對唔會玩，仲會去打負評比你<br />\n即係你賣一兩次廣告，出到啲賣點我都仲會睇下玩下，你日日播啲垃圾廣告只會增加我對依隻game嘅討厭。<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8867cd66c4f6419e27049d5f00c52817033f309a","tid":45004,"uid":8324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:19:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挽</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a945227b30de1d023cb3ba0ed428260f16d824f","tid":45004,"uid":22864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"我叫香蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9639da15f92bc70c60ce2f4325a57611412ae5b","tid":45004,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挽</span></span></blockquote><br />\n挽乜?"},{"pid":"54a128ab7d2eb25fbfbe27310a7514e06ddd83a7","tid":45004,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挽</span></span></blockquote><br />\n挽乜?</blockquote><br />\n我見到，sor ，係好玩好玩"},{"pid":"2aeba3ec0b5f0062172b8ce64b94786964be3b84","tid":45004,"uid":4387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"挽挽挽 挽你老母咩<br />\n你收皮佢都未收皮呀<br />\n隻game擺明出俾你呢啲小學雞玩"},{"pid":"4f172946e22ab842c2e4d57dc52fe8